			<div class="box" id="second-box"></div>
			<p class="box-header">Follow your favorites.</p>
			<p class="box-info">Backpack lets you follow your favorite developers so you'll be the first to know when they publish new videos. In addition, you can follow tags to stay on the cutting edge of all your most used technologies.</p>
