<div id="features-container">
	<div id="features-960">
		<div class="feature-column">
			<div class="feature">
				<div class="feature-icon" id="feature-icon-one"></div>
				<h4>Unlimited Storage</h4>
				<p class="feature-description">We never limit your videos by size or length, and you can upload all of your screencasts in pure HD - for free. Feel free to upload your entire catalog of tutorials and sharing them with the Backpack community.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature">
				<div class="feature-icon" id="feature-icon-two"></div>
				<h4>Embeddable Player</h4>
				<p class="feature-description">Using just a line of code, you can embed any video on your website or blog. Users can pay for videos directly in the Player, and all payments will still be processed through Backpack.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="feature-column">
			<div class="feature">
				<div class="feature-icon" id="feature-icon-three"></div>
				<h4>Video Library</h4>
				<p class="feature-description">Bookmark any free or purchased video with one click and view your entire Library with ease. Sorted by author, date, or tag, keep your purchases and favorite videos organized in one place.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature">
				<div class="feature-icon" id="feature-icon-four"></div>
				<h4>Watch Anywhere</h4>
				<p class="feature-description">Our website is fully responsive. Whether you're on a Retina Macbook, a tablet, or just your phone, you can always access your entire Backpack Library with ease.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="feature-column">
			<div class="feature">
				<div class="feature-icon" id="feature-icon-five"></div>
				<h4>Show Notes</h4>
				<p class="feature-description">If you don't have time to watch the whole video or you just forgot your headphones at home, most Backpack videos have a full Notes section with screenshots and code samples to explore at your leisure.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature">
				<div class="feature-icon" id="feature-icon-six"></div>
				<h4>Accept Payments</h4>
				<p class="feature-description">Backpack uses secure Stripe technology to process payments to and from users. All major credit cards are accepted, and if you sell videos, your balance is deposited weekly directly to your bank account.</p>
